## **4. `/common/` Directory**

Contains only **infrastructure-level utilities** shared across services.

| Folder | Responsibility |
|---------|----------------|
| `loggers/` | JSON logging setup |
| `errors/` | Base error classes |
| `middleware/` | JWT, tracing, unified error handling |
| `constants/` | Error codes, HTTP statuses |
| `types/` | Shared type definitions |
| `domain/` *(optional)* | Shared lightweight models |

**Rules:**
- вњ… Used only by services
- вќЊ No business logic or ORM models
- вќЊ No REST routes
- вќЊ No imports from `/services/`

