## **5. Naming Rules**

| Entity | Format | Example |
|---------|---------|----------|
| Files, dirs, vars, funcs | `snake_case` | `user_service.py`, `calculate_velocity()` |
| Classes | `PascalCase` | `UserCreate`, `BaseServiceError` |
| Constants | `UPPER_CASE` | `MAX_RETRIES` |
| DB Schemas | `snake_case` | `auth`, `raw_jira_cloud`, `clean_jira`, `bi_metrics` |
| Tables | `snake_case` | `users`, `projects` |
| Columns | `snake_case` | `user_id`, `created_at` |
| Foreign Keys | `<table>_id` | `project_id`, `user_id` |
| Indexes | `idx_<table>_<column>` | `idx_users_email` |
| Celery Tasks | `verb_noun_task` | `import_jira_issues_task` |
| Prefect Flows | `verb_noun_flow` | `transform_etl_pipeline_flow` |
| API Endpoints | plural, `snake_case` | `/api/v1/users`, `/api/v1/projects/{id}/issues` |

